日期</a>。</p><p>门票于本周六（8 月 31 日）上午 9 点（英国夏令时）开始公开发售 – <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里</a>（英国）和<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.ie%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Doasis" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>（爱尔兰）购买门票。粉丝们还可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-share-details-of-reunion-tour-pre-sale-ballot-sign-up-here-3787970">报名参加投票，以便在英国夏令时间今天 (28) 晚上 7 点之前周五 (30) 进行预售</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，Ticketmaster 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-2025-ticketmaster-share-strict-rules-for-buying-tickets-3787960">向那些希望获得即将到来的团圆巡演门票的人分享了严格的规则</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">周五（8 月 30 日），乐队发布了 1994 年开创性首张专辑《Definitely Maybe》的 30 周年纪念再版，</a>此前，备受期待的巡演消息传出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-will-reportedly-make-more-than-400million-3787259">据报道预计将赚得 4 亿英镑</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3775018" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3775018" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3775018" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270.jpg" alt="绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Oasis@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3775018" class="wp-caption-text">绿洲乐队的利亚姆·加拉格尔和诺埃尔·加拉格尔。图片来源：Fiona Hanson – PA Images/PA Images/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>这不是我们今年第一次听到《蜗牛邮报》的封面。本月早些时候，她分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smashing-pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins 乐队</a>的《Tonight, Tonight》的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-snail-mails-euphoric-cover-of-smashing-pumpkins-tonight-tonight-3780200">欢快版本</a>，2 月，在巴尔的摩<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snail-mail-announces-2023-valentine-fest-residency-in-baltimore-3348084">情人节音乐节驻场演出的第四晚</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-snail-mail-and-mac-demarco-cover-talking-heads-this-must-be-the-place-at-valentine-fest-3398914">这位歌手与 Mac DeMarco 联手翻唱了 Talking Heads 1983 年的经典歌曲《Tonight, Tonight》。这一定是这个地方（天真的旋律）&#39;</a> 。</p><p>她还与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/waxahatchee">Waxahatchee</a>一起翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-waxahatchee-snail-mail-cover-the-killers-when-you-were-young-3399304">When You Were Young</a> 》，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-snail-mail-and-soccer-mommy-cover-avril-lavigne-3397722">在巴尔的摩的一场音乐会上与 Soccer Mommy 一起翻唱了艾薇儿·拉维尼 (Avril Lavigne) 的《I&#39;m With You》</a> ，并为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muse">Muse</a>的《Starlight》献上了精彩表演。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-snail-mail-cover-muses-starlight-during-us-tour-3290023">在她 2022 年美国头条巡演期间</a>前往。</p><p>去年九月，Snail Mail 和 DeMarco 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snail-mail-mac-demarco-cuckholds-refrain-peppermint-patty-3312948">分享了一首名为“A Cuckhold&#39;s Refrain”的新歌，这首歌归功于一个名为 Peppermint Patty 的项目</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-snail-mail-celebrate-oasis-reunion-with-gnarly-cover-of-supersonic-in-nycs-central-park-3788392">Watch Snail Mail 庆祝 Oasis 在纽约中央公园重聚的帖子《Supersonic》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
